  "title": "Kitchen Crew / Sandwich Maker (5D/Bagel & Sandwich) - JT",
  "description": "<p><strong>💰$3,000 + $250 Transport Allowance</strong><br /><strong>⏲ 5D 6/7am to 3.30pm</strong><br /><strong>📍Islandwide (Tanjong Pagar/Novena/Holland Village/Joo Chiat/Punggol)</strong><br /><strong>📍Training at Tanjong Pagar for first 1 months</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and assemble sandwiches, burgers, and other menu items in the hot kitchen according to company standards.</li><li>Manage food preparation, cooking, and plating to ensure quality, hygiene, and consistency.</li><li>Handle counter service, including taking customer orders, processing payments, and serving food.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen, counter, and dining areas in compliance with food safety standards.</li><li>Replenish ingredients and supplies as required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Preferably experience in F&B or fast food service, training will be provided.</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Good communication and customer service skills.</li><li>Team player with a positive attitude.</li><li>Willing to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays.</li></ul><p>Company Name: Nala Employment Pte Ltd | License No.: 16C8302<br />EA Personnel Name: Tan Zhi Ning<br />EA Personnel No: R23116671</p>",
